{
  "stem": "22803.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, well, up to that time, as I said, things became that you were more uneasy and more regulations against Jews.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had to take all the silver and turn it in, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had to--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had to-- well, businesses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I told you the maids could not stay.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And businesses were failing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And people-- doctors couldn't practice anymore, or rather not on non-Jewish patients.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that is-- it was doing worse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they still had, you know, had customers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's-- lawyers were prohibited, you see.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People that were working for the state as-- as [NON-ENGLISH]-- what's [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, the function of the government-- government employees lost their jobs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So a private business, as long as the customers were still buying, was still sustainable.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At that time, my mother started.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was never working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She would go in Saturday mornings with my fathers, I guess maybe to work on the books or whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So eventually, you know, just economic conditions became worse for Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What else did you ask me?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, I was asking you what you remembered about Kristallnacht and what happened that night?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, oh, that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "OK, to lead up to that, is a-- I was, at that time, to school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had six years of high school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, Germany, I guess, already preparing for war, cut the school years, I guess, to get people to go in the army or whatever.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so after the fifth year, we graduated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my parents at that time wanted me to go some more to school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went to this one year to that for women's studies, where I explained to you where I learned to cook and such things.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
